attributes.title: The app has COVID-19
attributes.review: Why is this app the worst that was ever made? Because I took this app to the app doctor at Best Buy and Dr. Doctor said that the app had COVID. At first, I blamed Trump because he never wears his mask and probably infected the app with COVID himself. Or maybe he gave it whatever drugs he’s telling people to take that experts disapprove of. But then, I realized... it was me. It was completely my fault. Why? Because I took the app to the app doctor, Dr. Doctor. It is because since I took it to get tested, it now has the virus. Our beloved president said that there are more cases because of testing, so by that logic, taking my app to get tested allowed the app to get the virus. Because if I never went to go get it tested, it would have never been sick. So it’s my fault. That is why this app if getting terrible ratings. My apologies. Please forgive me.
